text: Josie and the Pussycats is a 2001 musical comedy movie based on the Archie Comics group of the same name. It was released by Universal and didn't do well at the box office. It became a cult movie. ==Cast== *Rachael Leigh Cook as Josie *Tara Reid *Rosario Dawson as Valerie Brown *Parker Posey *Alan Cumming *Seth Green ==Other websites== * Category:2001 musical movies Category:2001 comedy movies Category:2000s buddy movies Category:American musical comedy movies Category:Canadian musical movies Category:Canadian comedy movies Category:English-language movies Category:Cult movies Category:Female buddy movies Category:Movies based on comic book characters
